.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B CONSOLE
.ad
.RS 24n
.rt
If set, root can login on that device only. This does not prevent execution
of remote commands with
.BR rsh (1).
Comment out this line to allow login by
root.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B PASSREQ
.ad
.RS 24n
.rt
Determines if login requires a non-null password.
.RE

